{"tid":2459181,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是貴午 燒烏頭配秦國蘆筍及酸豆檸檬牛油醬汁","createTime":"2021-03-24T03:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T19:11:03.000Z","uid":33359,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c76cf689d93151c10ca1eedfa1c4a70fdb7f79e1","tid":2459181,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/szMdvpv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FszMdvpv.jpg&h=6c11c55d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jD4yvpz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjD4yvpz.jpg&h=d244c008&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6wi7zRf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wi7zRf.jpg&h=decc1c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfXPObi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfXPObi.jpg&h=29276f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYY0apF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYY0apF.jpg&h=b6775cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日難得平日放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢間鋪其實睇咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前有報道話$98半自助餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到我依家得閒去嗰陣已經加到$148<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主菜都係預佢細份因為主要都係食半自助餐食到飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n烏頭魚本身係比較肥嘅魚嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我呢條應該係岩岩做完168斷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n油脂香唔係好夠同埋啲肉都煎得有啲老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係個醬汁味道係唔錯嘅同烏頭魚幾夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁其他果幾碟全部都係半自助餐任食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沙律類全部都唔錯尤其秦式沙律幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熟食就完全冇肉全部都係蔬菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係蔬菜食落都幾新鮮唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甜品就偏少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前見佢有朱古力噴泉但係而家得返一碗朱古力醬自己淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個泡芙就咁食怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外層淋哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個filling 應該係mascarpone?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少食芝士唔是好識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我懷疑佢係比我淋朱古力醬上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淋完個味先叫做正常少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n芝士蛋糕唔錯唔會太鹹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整體來講佢加咗價但食嘅嘢又少咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試一次就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a336f9886c438594ca5a5b5a84975db4705aaf9","tid":2459181,"uid":6653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:59:30.000Z","msg":"有米師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199bba1c0d2e12ac0b308fddaf3b2d4ed90071d4","tid":2459181,"uid":369075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"印度公司今日休息？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9f91b8bd36787ce268a796b9d738c3217af568","tid":2459181,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:00:35.000Z","msg":"TLDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmo